DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		VALUES('DimCustomer'[EnglishOccupation])

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'DimCustomer'[EnglishOccupation], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	'DimCustomer'[EnglishOccupation]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		VALUES('DimProduct'[Color])

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'DimProduct'[Color], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	'DimProduct'[Color]

SELECT 
TOP (101) [t4].[Color]
FROM 
(
(
select [$Outer].[ProductKey] as [ProductKey],
    [$Outer].[EnglishProductName] as [ProductName],
    [$Outer].[Color] as [Color],
    [$Outer].[ModelName] as [ModelName],
    [$Outer].[EnglishProductSubcategoryName] as [ProductSubcategory],
    [$Inner].[EnglishProductCategoryName] as [ProductCategory]
from 
(
    select [$Outer].[ProductKey] as [ProductKey],
        [$Outer].[ProductAlternateKey] as [ProductAlternateKey],
        [$Outer].[ProductSubcategoryKey2] as [ProductSubcategoryKey2],
        [$Outer].[WeightUnitMeasureCode] as [WeightUnitMeasureCode],
        [$Outer].[SizeUnitMeasureCode] as [SizeUnitMeasureCode],
        [$Outer].[EnglishProductName] as [EnglishProductName],
        [$Outer].[SpanishProductName] as [SpanishProductName],
        [$Outer].[FrenchProductName] as [FrenchProductName],
        [$Outer].[StandardCost] as [StandardCost],
        [$Outer].[FinishedGoodsFlag] as [FinishedGoodsFlag],
        [$Outer].[Color] as [Color],
        [$Outer].[SafetyStockLevel] as [SafetyStockLevel],
        [$Outer].[ReorderPoint] as [ReorderPoint],
        [$Outer].[ListPrice] as [ListPrice],
        [$Outer].[Size] as [Size],
        [$Outer].[SizeRange] as [SizeRange],
        [$Outer].[Weight] as [Weight],
        [$Outer].[DaysToManufacture] as [DaysToManufacture],
        [$Outer].[ProductLine] as [ProductLine],
        [$Outer].[DealerPrice] as [DealerPrice],
        [$Outer].[Class] as [Class],
        [$Outer].[Style] as [Style],
        [$Outer].[ModelName] as [ModelName],
        [$Outer].[LargePhoto] as [LargePhoto],
        [$Outer].[EnglishDescription] as [EnglishDescription],
        [$Outer].[FrenchDescription] as [FrenchDescription],
        [$Outer].[ChineseDescription] as [ChineseDescription],
        [$Outer].[ArabicDescription] as [ArabicDescription],
        [$Outer].[HebrewDescription] as [HebrewDescription],
        [$Outer].[ThaiDescription] as [ThaiDescription],
        [$Outer].[GermanDescription] as [GermanDescription],
        [$Outer].[JapaneseDescription] as [JapaneseDescription],
        [$Outer].[TurkishDescription] as [TurkishDescription],
        [$Outer].[StartDate] as [StartDate],
        [$Outer].[EndDate] as [EndDate],
        [$Outer].[Status] as [Status],
        [$Inner].[EnglishProductSubcategoryName] as [EnglishProductSubcategoryName],
        [$Inner].[ProductCategoryKey] as [ProductCategoryKey2]
    from 
    (
        select [_].[ProductKey] as [ProductKey],
            [_].[ProductAlternateKey] as [ProductAlternateKey],
            [_].[ProductSubcategoryKey] as [ProductSubcategoryKey2],
            [_].[WeightUnitMeasureCode] as [WeightUnitMeasureCode],
            [_].[SizeUnitMeasureCode] as [SizeUnitMeasureCode],
            [_].[EnglishProductName] as [EnglishProductName],
            [_].[SpanishProductName] as [SpanishProductName],
            [_].[FrenchProductName] as [FrenchProductName],
            [_].[StandardCost] as [StandardCost],
            [_].[FinishedGoodsFlag] as [FinishedGoodsFlag],
            [_].[Color] as [Color],
            [_].[SafetyStockLevel] as [SafetyStockLevel],
            [_].[ReorderPoint] as [ReorderPoint],
            [_].[ListPrice] as [ListPrice],
            [_].[Size] as [Size],
            [_].[SizeRange] as [SizeRange],
            [_].[Weight] as [Weight],
            [_].[DaysToManufacture] as [DaysToManufacture],
            [_].[ProductLine] as [ProductLine],
            [_].[DealerPrice] as [DealerPrice],
            [_].[Class] as [Class],
            [_].[Style] as [Style],
            [_].[ModelName] as [ModelName],
            [_].[LargePhoto] as [LargePhoto],
            [_].[EnglishDescription] as [EnglishDescription],
            [_].[FrenchDescription] as [FrenchDescription],
            [_].[ChineseDescription] as [ChineseDescription],
            [_].[ArabicDescription] as [ArabicDescription],
            [_].[HebrewDescription] as [HebrewDescription],
            [_].[ThaiDescription] as [ThaiDescription],
            [_].[GermanDescription] as [GermanDescription],
            [_].[JapaneseDescription] as [JapaneseDescription],
            [_].[TurkishDescription] as [TurkishDescription],
            [_].[StartDate] as [StartDate],
            [_].[EndDate] as [EndDate],
            [_].[Status] as [Status]
        from [dbo].[DimProduct] as [_]
        where [_].[FinishedGoodsFlag] = 1
    ) as [$Outer]
    left outer join [dbo].[DimProductSubcategory] as [$Inner] on ([$Outer].[ProductSubcategoryKey2] = [$Inner].[ProductSubcategoryKey])
) as [$Outer]
left outer join [dbo].[DimProductCategory] as [$Inner] on ([$Outer].[ProductCategoryKey2] = [$Inner].[ProductCategoryKey])
)
)
 AS [t4]
GROUP BY [t4].[Color]
ORDER BY [t4].[Color]
ASC

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('DimCustomer'[Country], "TotalAmountInt", 'FactInternetSales'[TotalAmountInt])

		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, 'DimCustomer'[Country], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'DimCustomer'[Country]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('DimDate'[CalendarYear], "TotalAmountRes", 'FactResellerSales'[TotalAmountRes])

	__DS0BodyLimited
